    <div class='contentArea'>
      <div class='elements uielement infobox'>
        <h1>What are elements?</h1>
        <hr />
        <p>Elements are the building blocks of our payment screens.  They can be enabled or disabled, made visible or invisible, depending on your requirements.</p>
        <p>This page may be used to add or remove form elements or entire sections of the form.  You do this by adding element controls on the right to override the default settings.</p>
      </div>
      <div class='uielement data'>
        <div class='hidden'>
          <div class='template control'>
            <form>
              <div class='settings'>
                <input type='hidden' name='original_identifier' value='' />
                <input type='hidden' name='original_category' value='' />
                <input type='hidden' name='original_language' value='' />
                <span class='setting'>
                  <label><span class='labelText'>MetaPhrase Category:</span>
                    <select type='text' name='category' /><select>
                  </label>
                </span> 
                <span class='setting'>
                  <label><span class='labelText'>MetaPhrase Text Key:</span>
                    <select type='text' name='identifier' /></select>
                  </label>
                </span> 
                <span class='setting inline'>
                  <label><span class='labelText'>Text:</span>
                    <textarea name='text'></textarea>
                  </label>
                </span> 
                <span class='setting'>
                  <label span class='labelText'>Language:</span>
                    <select name='language'>
                      <option value='EN-US'>EN-US</option>>
                    </select>
                </span>
              </div>
              <div class='buttons'>
                <input class='setButton' name='set' type='button' value='Set' />
                <input class='removeButton' name='remove' type='button' value='Remove' />
              </div>
              <div class='controllerSpinner'></div>
              <div class='clearFloat'></div>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
        <input type='button' id='addControl' value="Add MetaPhrase Override">
        <div id='controls'></div>
      </div>
      <div class='clearFloat'> </div>
